Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:58.04,Typesetting,,0,0,0,,{=17}{\fnCC EmpireStateGothic\fscx200\pos(960,628)\blur0.7\c&HE58600&}Prazer, me chamo Lilly!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.43,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom dia, irmã!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom dia, Fuu.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.31,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu tive um sonho estranho.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 99,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.15,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu deveria ver como as meninas estão.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.99,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Claro, por favor.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.33,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você ainda tá de pijama?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.17,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom dia, mãe!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.04,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos eu posso te dar nota\N máxima em cumprimentos!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.96,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Obrigada pelo café!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.38,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você já tá indo, Rui?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.84,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Estou responsável pela classe hoje.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.14,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bem quente hoje, \Nentão toma cuidado.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.56,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu vou. Vai ficar tudo bem.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.56,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.14,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vá com cuidado.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.52,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Fuu, se vista logo!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.94,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bom...
Dialogue: 99,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tchau, mãe!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:49.92,0:03:53.17,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, vem comigo para a\N piscina nas férias de verão?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.30,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não pode?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:59.18,0:04:02.81,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Preciso usar as férias para poder\N colocar meus estudos em dia.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.81,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você vai estudar?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.06,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Caramba, que responsável!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até mais.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.27,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.20,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente queria ir\N pra piscina com ela....
Dialogue: 99,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.57,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, desculpa!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.28,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E aí, Fuu?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.58,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sho-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.58,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você realmente nunca muda.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom dia!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.75,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom dia.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.71,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Como vai a Rui?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.54,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ela está ótima!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.96,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah... bom saber...
Dialogue: 99,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.63,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, vamos brincar juntos \Nnas férias de verão!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.72,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você pode me ensinar basquete!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.18,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera aí.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.35,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não posso. Vou ter uma partida pelo clube.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.14,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:44.97,0:04:45.81,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até mais.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:52.15,0:04:57.57,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Poxa! Tá todo mundo ocupado ultimamente, \Nentão ninguém tem tempo de brincar comigo.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.65,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não era assim antes...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:00.95,0:05:04.66,Italic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Minha irmã sempre cantava algo pra mim.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:00.03,0:05:04.66,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,Eu rezei para as estrelas
Dialogue: 99,0:05:04.66,0:05:09.46,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,que brilhavam intensamente lá no céu.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:09.46,0:05:13.17,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,E acima das nuvens, tão fofas,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.38,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,Rui?!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.64,Italic,,0,0,0,,Mas desde que ela foi internada\N por conta de uma doença,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.97,Italic,,0,0,0,,ela perdeu toda a energia que tinha.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:27.22,0:05:30.14,Italic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aparentemente não tem nada\N de errado com ela, mas...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.06,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Pra onde foi todo mundo?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.78,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu me sinto um pouco sozinha...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.03,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E o verão logo vai estar aqui...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.37,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Fuu-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.16,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você vai se atrasar.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.87,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,B-Bom dia!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:56.54,0:06:01.42,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Como puderam observar na nossa atividade,\N os girinos eclodem de ovos de rã.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.05,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Então como acham que os peixes medaka nascem?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.76,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eles também nascem de ovos.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.56,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nós iremos observá-los em um tanque...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.27,Italic,,0,0,0,,Aquilo é uma espaçonave?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:13.90,0:06:19.15,Italic,,0,0,0,,Será que vieram aqui me abduzir\N por conta do meu tédio?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.74,Italic,,0,0,0,,Ah, até parece.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.71,Italic,,0,0,0,,É mesmo uma espaçonave!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.88,Italic,,0,0,0,,Por favor, vem pra cá!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.67,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.51,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.01,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.09,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sensei, olha lá pra fora!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.47,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Mas não tem nada lá.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.18,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Uma espaçonave acabou de passar, eu juro!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você viu?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.52,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não. Não vi nada.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.52,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san, por favor, sente-se.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.65,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Desculpa...
Dialogue: 99,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.69,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vamos retomar a aula.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.70,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, quer ir para o karaokê depois da escola?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Claro, quero sim!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.45,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,No lugar de sempre?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.28,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.41,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, vamos chamar a Rui-chan.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:12.41,0:07:12.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bom.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.37,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Quer vir com a gente, Nonoyama-san?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.71,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Rui-chan, a gente vai no karaokê! Topa?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.21,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Desculpa, eu não canto muito.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.51,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Poxa.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:24.51,0:07:28.64,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Entendi. Esqueci que você não gosta\N de lugares barulhentos, Nonoyama-san.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.22,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A gente marca outra hora.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.06,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Desculpa mesmo...
Dialogue: 99,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.31,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até amanhã!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até amanhã.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.23,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Fuu-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.94,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu juro que eu vi uma.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.36,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá falando da nave?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.57,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ainda tá procurando por ela?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:48.57,0:07:53.37,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sério, aquilo era enorme! \NComo ninguém mais viu?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.66,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Era {\i1}desse{\i0} tamanho!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.87,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E passou bem na frente da janela!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.21,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza disso?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.63,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A gente não viu nada.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.67,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Quê? Mas tava voando bem de frente...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.39,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que gatos esquisitos.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.72,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.10,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, deixa pra lá.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.65,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu cuido das entregas amanhã.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.15,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá fazendo calor demais.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.73,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, querido!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.99,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Obrigada pela comida.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.20,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.03,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu algo legal na sua escola hoje?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu uma coisa tão incrível na minha!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.16,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Hoje...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.12,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Bom, meu professor...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.08,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,...disse que hoje era o aniversário dele.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.00,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eh? E aí?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.59,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Acho que foi só isso.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.88,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.68,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E o que foi que aconteceu \Nde incrível com você, Fuu?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.31,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não, não foi nada.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.68,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bom...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.93,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vou tomar banho.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.19,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bom!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.65,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Por que você não vai com ela, Fuu?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.23,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tô de boa.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.36,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Elas costumavam entrar juntas, não é?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.86,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Talvez seja a idade.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.99,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não é isso...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.30,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ei, maninha, espera!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.71,Diálogo-Alt,,0,0,0,,Eu rezei para as estrelas
Dialogue: 99,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.93,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Foi só um sonho...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.64,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu rezei para...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.73,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Queria ouvir a Onee-chan cantar de novo...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.77,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Fuu!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.40,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Já tô acordada!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:33.07,0:10:36.03,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,2 metros de fita vermelha custam 32 ienes.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.45,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,1,6 metros de fita azul também custam 32 ienes.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:40.95,0:10:48.00,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Qual é o preço de 1 metro de cada fita?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.17,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nenhum sinal dela.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:57.43,0:11:01.35,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar pela fita vermelha.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.98,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Pra achar o preço de 1 metro,\N é só dividir o valor pelo comprimento.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:06.98,0:11:11.11,Italic,,0,0,0,,Eu sinto que se eu conseguir encontrar \Naquilo de novo, talvez as coisas mudem.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.49,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vai viajar pra algum lugar nas férias de verão?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.82,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vou pra casa da minha avó! \NFica lá na praia!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.49,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eh? Que inveja!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.20,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E você?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.12,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sei lá... talvez eu vá pra praia também?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.83,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.16,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até amanhã!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.37,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, é... tchau!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.55,Italic,,0,0,0,,Por favor, nave espacial, vem pra cá de novo!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.59,Italic,,0,0,0,,Eu tô implorando!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Voltou!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.57,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.68,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A vista daqui é maravilhosa.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.51,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá quente demais...
Dialogue: 99,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.18,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Chamam de "verão" aqui!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.43,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Olhem. O sol está se pondo.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Deixe me ver.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que bonito!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.73,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,É brilhante demais...
Dialogue: 99,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.44,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ué?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tem uma criança correndo atrás da gente.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Por favor, me espera!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.45,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,É a de ontem.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.32,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Aquela pirralha!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:42.66,0:12:46.54,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Estranho... humanos não deveriam\N conseguir ver essa nave.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.92,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Espera por mim!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.46,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.72,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Por favor...
Dialogue: 99,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tô quase lá...
Dialogue: 99,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.70,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.28,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.49,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.75,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, aqueles gatos de ontem!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.12,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.46,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você tá bem?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.88,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eles falaram!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.63,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sim, falamos.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.51,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu consegui... chegar na nave...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.72,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Cof, cof.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.97,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Quem seria você?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.81,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Nonoyama Fuu.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:30.81,0:14:34.23,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Aqui é uma nave especial, né?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.36,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,É uma nave mágica.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:36.36,0:14:41.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Meeter. \NVim da terra mágica Estrela Felix.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.90,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Estamos visitando este planeta como turistas.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.11,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, eu...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.99,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu precisava entrar nessa nave, porque...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.21,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,do jeito que as coisas estão,\N minha irmã, o Sho-chan,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.50,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,todo mundo vai crescer,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.75,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,e só eu vou ficar pra trás...
Dialogue: 99,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.14,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu só queria que minha irmã sorrisse mais,
Dialogue: 99,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.85,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,mas não sei como ajudá-la.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.64,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E por isso...
Dialogue: 99,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.44,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você quer mudar as coisas, não quer?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Se seus sentimentos forem fortes, \Nvocê pode usar magia.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.20,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você quer tentar usá-la?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.54,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.05,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que linda!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.56,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Isso é um Coração de Vidro,\N e ele é a fonte de sua magia.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.89,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Humanos só podem usar magia por um ano.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:56.89,0:16:02.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E você não pode deixar nenhum \Noutro humano descobrir sobre ela.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.86,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nem minha mãe e meu pai?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.95,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nem mesmo minha irmã?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.45,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ninguém.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:11.83,0:16:16.71,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Se seguir as regras, você poderá fazer\N coisas incríveis com sua magia.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.96,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Quero que me mostre o que\N vai desejar fazer com isso.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.46,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,E como eu uso isso?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.47,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Dê um toquezinho e diga "litto". {eu to ouvindo pitto}
Dialogue: 99,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.26,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Litto!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.81,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Uma varinha mágica?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.98,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Agora, tendo essa varinha em mão,\N diga as palavras mágicas.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.53,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,As que você imaginou.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.49,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tente.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.24,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tá bom!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.00,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Pam pam {\i1}power{\i0}!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.09,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu tô alta agora!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.51,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você se transformou na sua forma ideal!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.01,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você ficou linda!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.85,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você pode usar essa varinha pra\N lançar qualquer tipo de magia.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Qualquer tipo?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.35,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Desde que você realmente deseje.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.40,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Essa nave chama muita atenção.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.20,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Outras pessoas não conseguem ver!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.41,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.16,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de magia eu faço?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:19.75,0:18:23.67,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tem que ser algo que todo \Nmundo possa aproveitar!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.21,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:26.21,0:18:31.30,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,encha o céu com fogos\N de artifício gigantes!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que isso?!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.86,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tinha algum show de fogos marcado pra hoje?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.82,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Não fiquei sabendo de nada.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:57.82,0:19:01.08,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, Rui! Olha lá fora!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.45,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você vai ficar supresa!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.96,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.09,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que lindo...
Dialogue: 99,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.27,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A magia acabou.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.48,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Foi incrível.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.98,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nada mal.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.28,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Excelente trabalho.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.32,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Foi muito bom, considerando que foi sua\N primeira vez. Os fogos estavam lindos.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.03,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.66,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.04,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,É melhor eu ir agora.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.83,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vou deixar esses dois com você, \Ncaso aconteça alguma coisa.
Comment: 99,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.21,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.38,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Se tiver dúvidas, pode perguntar pra eles.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.04,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,A gente ajuda.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.09,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você já vai embora?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.72,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Você deve manter sua magia em segredo dos\N humanos, não importa o que aconteça.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:57.76,0:20:02.39,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Nos veremos de novo daqui a \Num ano, no Festival{shukusai} da Magia.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.90,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Uma lição{shukudai} de magia? {te vira, haise}
Dialogue: 99,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.49,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, já tá escuro. \NTenho que ir pra casa.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.32,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Como eu volto ao normal?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.91,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,É só dizer "tohri".
Dialogue: 99,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.37,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Tohri!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ei, tem alguma magia pra me fazer\N voltar pra casa mais rápido?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.30,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ou talvez que me faça voar?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.55,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Se errar, você cai.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.55,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eh, isso não é nada bom!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.80,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Cheguei!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.27,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Por favor, deixa eu ficar com eles!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.77,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu juro que vou fazer todos os \Nmeus deveres e minhas tarefas!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.02,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que você acha?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.69,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,São gatos bem estranhos, mas por que não?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.24,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Cuide bem deles.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.78,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, pai, mãe!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.16,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Que nomes vai dar pra eles?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.87,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Azuki e Uguisu!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.13,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.92,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Falando nisso, você viu, Fuu?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.63,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Acabou de ter uma show de fogos.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.84,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,V-Vi sim.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.60,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vou trocar de roupa.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.98,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Azuki, não é por aí!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.07,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.53,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:39.99,0:21:43.11,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eu trouxe eles dois pra\N poder criá-los aqui em casa.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.53,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.29,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,São tão fofos.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:51.58,0:21:56.63,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Acabou de ter uma grande chuva \Nde fogos ainda agora. Você viu?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.34,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Vi.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:03.47,0:22:06.05,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,Eram muito bonitos.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.11,Diálogo,,0,0,0,,As coisas vão ficar divertidas a partir de amanhã
