Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.45,0:22:27.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{=20}{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Coragem está em dois mundos, juntos agora
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.08,0:22:27.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Essa é a prova!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}É isso que nos conecta
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Todos sorriem para garotas bonitas
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.79,0:22:34.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Meu Sonho!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Só quero saber o que o futuro guarda
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.59,0:22:38.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Sozinha!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.21,0:22:42.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mesmo que as estrelas em um céu sem lua
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}ainda brilhem
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Sem magia!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.93,0:22:49.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mesmo que as nuvens em um céu sem sol
Dialogue: 2,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}ainda sigam seu caminho
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Eu continuo tristemente
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Que parecia que sempre ficaria ao meu lado)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}a procurar por você
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.57,0:23:02.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vou enquadrar uma foto de nós dois e pendurar
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vou organizar tudo do meu jeito, como eu quiser, como realmente é
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.82,0:23:10.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Nossa sintonia: somar, subtrair, multiplicar, dividir por...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.24,0:23:10.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Eu amo tudo isso!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Me chamando, te chamando
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(E Você)
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Quero subir as escadas do futuro com você
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6\i1}Lucky lucky shiny{\i0}, nossos corações vibrando em sonhos
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Se amanhã o céu estiver limpo, vai ficar tudo bem
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Talvez eu esteja um pouco triste e fraco
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.47,0:23:29.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Mas Feliz!)
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mas quando estou com você, me sinto salva
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Não existe tempo perdido
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vamos esperar a chuva passar
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.48,0:23:39.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Olha para o céu! Se fizer isso
